'''''Star Wars Insider'' 99''' was the 99th ''[[Star Wars Insider]]'' issue to be published, and the 7th issue to be published by [[Titan Magazines]].

==Contents==
===Departments===
*"Editor's Welcome" {{C|by [[Brian J. Robb]]}}
*"[[Com-Scan]]"
*"[[Best of StarWars.com]]"
*"[[Jawa's Corner]]"
**Books &mdash; It's a Mad, Mad, Mad, Mad Galaxy! {{C|by [[Jason Fry]]}}
**Comics &mdash; [[Star Wars: Rebellion: Small Victories|Unsung Heroes]] {{C|by [[Daniel Wallace]]}}
**Games &mdash; [[Star Wars Battlefront: Renegade Squadron|Start Wars!]] {{C|by Jonathan Wilkins}}
**Toys &mdash; Unconventional to Classic {{C|by [[Jeremy Beckett]]}}
**[[Star Wars Q&A|Q&A]] &mdash; The Secret Lives of Bounty Hunters {{C|by [[Leland Chee]]}}
**[[Scouting the Galaxy]] &mdash; If You Love ''Star Wars'', Always Believe 'Mam'! {{C|by [[Stephen J. Sansweet|Steve Sansweet]]}}
**[[International Collecting]] &mdash; The French Connection {{C|by [[Gus Lopez]]}}
**[[Set Piece]] &mdash; The ''Invisible Hand'': General Dooku's Quarters {{C|by [[Chris Trevas]]}}
**[[Padawan's Corner]] &mdash; How to Draw: Zuckuss {{C|by [[Cynthia Narcisi|Cynthia Cummens]]}}
**[[Indy Vault]] #7 {{C|by [[Jonathan W. Rinzler|J. W. Rinzler]]}}
**[[Comlink (department)|Comlink]]

===Features===
*"[[Tales of the Bounty Hunters (article)|Tales of the Bounty Hunters]]" {{C|by [[Daniel Wallace]]}}
*:<small>They may be minor characters onscreen, but beyond the six ''Star Wars'' files, bounty hunters have made a significant impact on that galaxy far, far away.</small>
*"[[The Ultimate Hunter]]" {{C|by [[Jonathan Wilkins]]}}
*:<small>''[[Star Wars Insider]]'' meets the man inside the iconic Boba Fett armor, [[Jeremy Bulloch]], and Boba's younger self, [[Daniel Logan]] from ''Attack of the Clones''.</small>
*"[[Bounty Hunters' Guild Handbook (article)|Bounty Hunters' Guild Handbook]]" {{C|by Jonathan Wilkins}}
*:<small>Do you have what it takes to be a bounty hunter? Check out our exclusive guide to the lifestyle and challenges of facing off against galactic bad guys!</small>
*"[[Feat of Clay: Inside Kotobukiya]]" {{C|by [[Shingo Nakagawa]], [[Mariki Kawamura]]}}
*:<small>Exclusive access to the making of Japanese company Kotobukiya's brand new series of bounty hunter figures. See high-end collectible's being created!</small>
*"[[Boba Begins]]" {{C|by [[Pete Vilmur]]}}
*:<small>Think you know when Boba Fett's first appearance was? Prepare to be surprised as we reveal the secret origins of this most enigmatic of bounty hunters.</small>
*"[[Ben Burtt: May The Sound Be with You!]]" {{C|by [[Pat Jankiewicz]]}}
*:<small>''Star Wars'' sound designer Ben Burtt talks Wookiees, alien languages, and the real Stary bebined the infamous Wilhelm scream!</small>
*"First Crack of the Whip!" {{C|by Ian Spelling}}
*:<small>As anticipation builds for nest spring's new Indiana Jones movie, Rick MeCallum and Sean Patrick Flanery look back at the Young Indy TV series.</small>

